    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "PORTLAND, OREGON, August 20th 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "Lt. Col. Donald L. Springer, Assistant Staff",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "Sir. Saw in the portland paper a short time ago in regards to",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "an article in regards to the so called flying disc having any basis",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "of fact. I can say am a [REDACTED] and was in the Mt Adams district",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "on June 24th the day [REDACTED] of Boise Idaho claims he saw a 66",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "formation of flying disc. And I saw the same flying objects at about",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "the same time. Having a telescope with me at the time I can asure you",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "they are real and noting like them I ever saw before they did not pass",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "verry high over where I was standing at the time plobly 1000 ft.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "they were Round about 30 foot in dimater tapering sharply to a point in",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "the head end in an oval shape. with a bright top surface. I did not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "hear any noise as you would from a plane. But there was an object in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "the tail end looked like a big hand of a clock shifting from side to",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "side like a big magenet. There speed as far as I know seemed to be",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "greater than anything I ever saw. Last veiw I got of the objects they",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "were standing on edge Banking in a Cloud.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Yours respectfully",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "/s/ [REDACTED] 66",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "A TRUE COPY:",
      "status": "image_matched"
